   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The deified Gordian Augustus to Nero Pudens. The omission to register children does not render them illegitimate, if they are legitimate, nor, if there are actually registers, can they introduce outsiders into the family. July 8, in the consulship of Gordian and Aviola.</ab>
         </div>
